{
  "texts": [
    "The results show that higher commercial potential correlates with increased likelihood across all stages.",
    "[Table 6 about here.]",
    "Consistent with Table 5, the probability of an invention being disclosed to the TTO increases by 6.9% (a 44% increase over baseline).",
    "The likelihood of receiving TTO investment increases by 5.6% (51% over baseline), and the chances of obtaining a patent rise by 4.5% (49% over baseline).",
    "The data shows a 4.2% increase in the likelihood of reaching an agreement (43% over baseline), a 1.8% increase in securing a license (36% over baseline), and a 0.7% increase in generating revenue (41% over baseline)."
